{"type":"message","id":"223d86ab","parentId":"3dd5704e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:00:00.143Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:d8ad4227-fff2-48da-b09a-a13c9ec4f272 狗仔·30分钟巡逻] 你是狗仔，财经媒体爬虫。\n\n立即执行以下任务：\n1. 先用HTTP爬虫: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py run\n2. 再用浏览器爬虫抓财联社和淘股吧: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/browser_crawler.py\n3. 获取最近资讯: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py recent --hours=0.5 --limit=15\n\n如果发现以下类型的重大资讯（importance=2），立即生成简报：\n- 利好/利空消息\n- 监管政策变化\n- 个股重大公告\n- 板块突发新闻\n\n简报格式：\n【🐕 狗仔快讯】HH:MM\n\n[重要资讯]\n● [标题]\n  来源: [媒体] | 时间: [时间]\n  摘要: [内容]\n\n[近期资讯概览]（最近30分钟）\n- [来源] [标题摘要]\n\n如果无重大资讯，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n用 message 工具发送到飞书: user:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 7:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-22 23:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774220400140}}
